name: Sam Singer
description:
Someone found him in the back closet of the building. He is obviously older based off of his design and material. My first thought was that we could use him to repair Fuzzy, but this guys voicebox is also fried. 
Then I got a message from the company saying they planned on keeping him to perform. They act as if we dont only have 2 weeks left to repair the others, now we have this guy. 4/28/95 - 14 days till opening
